  Locus:
    Page: 244
    Verse: 6
Tags:
  - Heaven & Hell
---
Heaven is under our feet as well as over our heads. ... When you travel
to the Celestial City, carry no letters of introduction -- When you knock,
ask to see God -- none of the servants.
